&lt;p&gt;The correct answer is &lt;u&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cabinet Ministers are a smaller group within the Council of Ministers&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/u&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/key-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;u style=&quot;font-size: 21px; font-weight: bolder; font-family: var(--bs-body-font-family); text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align);&quot;&gt;Key Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The Council of Ministers in India consists of three categories: &lt;strong&gt;Cabinet Ministers&lt;/strong&gt;, &lt;strong&gt;Ministers of State&lt;/strong&gt;, and &lt;strong&gt;Deputy Ministers&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cabinet Ministers&lt;/strong&gt; form the core group within the Council of Ministers and are responsible for major ministries such as Finance, Defense, External Affairs, and Home Affairs.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;While &lt;strong&gt;Ministers of State&lt;/strong&gt; assist Cabinet Ministers, they do not have the same rank and authority as Cabinet Ministers.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The Council of Ministers is appointed by the &lt;strong&gt;President of India&lt;/strong&gt; on the advice of the Prime Minister, not by the Chief Justice.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Not all members of the Council of Ministers are part of the Cabinet; only Cabinet Ministers are included in this smaller, more influential group.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/additional-information-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Additional Information&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Council of Ministers Structure:&lt;/strong&gt;

	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;The Council of Ministers is headed by the Prime Minister and includes Cabinet Ministers, Ministers of State, and Deputy Ministers.&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;Cabinet Ministers hold the highest rank and are involved in key decision-making processes.&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;Ministers of State may hold independent charge of ministries or assist Cabinet Ministers in their duties.&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;Deputy Ministers assist both Cabinet and State Ministers in their day-to-day responsibilities.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cabinet Minister Role:&lt;/strong&gt;
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;Cabinet Ministers are responsible for policy formulation and implementation for their respective ministries.&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;They are part of the Cabinet Committee and play a crucial role in advising the Prime Minister.&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;The Cabinet meets regularly to discuss and decide on matters of national importance.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Appointment and Tenure:&lt;/strong&gt;
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;The President appoints the Council of Ministers based on the Prime Minister&amp;rsquo;s advice.&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;Ministers serve at the pleasure of the President, meaning their tenure depends on the support of the Prime Minister.&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;The Prime Minister has the authority to reshuffle portfolios or recommend the removal of ministers.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Legislative and Executive Role:&lt;/strong&gt;
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;The Council of Ministers collectively functions as the executive authority of the government.&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;Cabinet Ministers represent the government in Parliament and are accountable for their ministries&amp;#39; actions.&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;They introduce bills, budgets, and policies in Parliament for approval and implementation.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The Correct Answer is&amp;nbsp;&lt;u&gt;&lt;strong&gt;130th&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/u&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/in_news.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;In News&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;India ranks 130th on Human Development Index, says UNDP 2025 report.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/key-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li data-end=&quot;311&quot; data-start=&quot;245&quot;&gt;
	&lt;p data-end=&quot;311&quot; data-start=&quot;247&quot;&gt;India ranked &lt;strong data-end=&quot;290&quot; data-start=&quot;260&quot;&gt;130th out of 193 countries&lt;/strong&gt; in the &lt;strong data-end=&quot;310&quot; data-start=&quot;298&quot;&gt;2025 HDR&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li data-end=&quot;396&quot; data-start=&quot;312&quot;&gt;
	&lt;p data-end=&quot;396&quot; data-start=&quot;314&quot;&gt;Report title: &lt;strong data-end=&quot;395&quot; data-start=&quot;328&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;A Matter of Choice: People and Possibilities in the Age of AI&amp;quot;&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li data-end=&quot;464&quot; data-start=&quot;397&quot;&gt;
	&lt;p data-end=&quot;464&quot; data-start=&quot;399&quot;&gt;Published by the &lt;strong data-end=&quot;463&quot; data-start=&quot;416&quot;&gt;United Nations Development Programme (UNDP)&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li data-end=&quot;534&quot; data-start=&quot;465&quot;&gt;
	&lt;p data-end=&quot;534&quot; data-start=&quot;467&quot;&gt;India&amp;rsquo;s &lt;strong data-end=&quot;491&quot; data-start=&quot;475&quot;&gt;HDI improved&lt;/strong&gt; from &lt;strong data-end=&quot;513&quot; data-start=&quot;497&quot;&gt;0.676 (2022)&lt;/strong&gt; to &lt;strong data-end=&quot;533&quot; data-start=&quot;517&quot;&gt;0.685 (2023)&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li data-end=&quot;645&quot; data-start=&quot;535&quot;&gt;
	&lt;p data-end=&quot;562&quot; data-start=&quot;537&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-end=&quot;561&quot; data-start=&quot;537&quot;&gt;Top-ranked countries&lt;/strong&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;

	&lt;ul data-end=&quot;645&quot; data-start=&quot;565&quot;&gt;
		&lt;li data-end=&quot;600&quot; data-start=&quot;565&quot;&gt;
		&lt;p data-end=&quot;600&quot; data-start=&quot;567&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-end=&quot;574&quot; data-start=&quot;567&quot;&gt;1st&lt;/strong&gt;: Iceland (HDI: &lt;strong data-end=&quot;599&quot; data-start=&quot;590&quot;&gt;0.972&lt;/strong&gt;)&lt;/p&gt;
		&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li data-end=&quot;620&quot; data-start=&quot;603&quot;&gt;
		&lt;p data-end=&quot;620&quot; data-start=&quot;605&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-end=&quot;612&quot; data-start=&quot;605&quot;&gt;2nd&lt;/strong&gt;: Norway&lt;/p&gt;
		&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li data-end=&quot;645&quot; data-start=&quot;623&quot;&gt;
		&lt;p data-end=&quot;645&quot; data-start=&quot;625&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-end=&quot;632&quot; data-start=&quot;625&quot;&gt;3rd&lt;/strong&gt;: Switzerland&lt;/p&gt;
		&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li data-end=&quot;706&quot; data-start=&quot;646&quot;&gt;
	&lt;p data-end=&quot;706&quot; data-start=&quot;648&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-end=&quot;665&quot; data-start=&quot;648&quot;&gt;Lowest-ranked&lt;/strong&gt;: &lt;strong data-end=&quot;682&quot; data-start=&quot;667&quot;&gt;South Sudan&lt;/strong&gt; (193rd, HDI: &lt;strong data-end=&quot;705&quot; data-start=&quot;696&quot;&gt;0.388&lt;/strong&gt;)&lt;/p&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li data-end=&quot;1026&quot; data-start=&quot;707&quot;&gt;
	&lt;p data-end=&quot;744&quot; data-start=&quot;709&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-end=&quot;743&quot; data-start=&quot;709&quot;&gt;India&amp;rsquo;s neighbouring countries&lt;/strong&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;

	&lt;ul data-end=&quot;1026&quot; data-start=&quot;747&quot;&gt;
		&lt;li data-end=&quot;853&quot; data-start=&quot;747&quot;&gt;
		&lt;p data-end=&quot;774&quot; data-start=&quot;749&quot;&gt;Ranked &lt;strong data-end=&quot;771&quot; data-start=&quot;756&quot;&gt;above India&lt;/strong&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;

		&lt;ul data-end=&quot;853&quot; data-start=&quot;779&quot;&gt;
			&lt;li data-end=&quot;799&quot; data-start=&quot;779&quot;&gt;
			&lt;p data-end=&quot;799&quot; data-start=&quot;781&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-end=&quot;797&quot; data-start=&quot;781&quot;&gt;China (75th)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
			&lt;/li&gt;
			&lt;li data-end=&quot;828&quot; data-start=&quot;804&quot;&gt;
			&lt;p data-end=&quot;828&quot; data-start=&quot;806&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-end=&quot;826&quot; data-start=&quot;806&quot;&gt;Sri Lanka (78th)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
			&lt;/li&gt;
			&lt;li data-end=&quot;853&quot; data-start=&quot;833&quot;&gt;
			&lt;p data-end=&quot;853&quot; data-start=&quot;835&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-end=&quot;853&quot; data-start=&quot;835&quot;&gt;Bhutan (127th)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
			&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;/ul&gt;
		&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li data-end=&quot;915&quot; data-start=&quot;856&quot;&gt;
		&lt;p data-end=&quot;886&quot; data-start=&quot;858&quot;&gt;Ranked &lt;strong data-end=&quot;883&quot; data-start=&quot;865&quot;&gt;equal to India&lt;/strong&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;

		&lt;ul data-end=&quot;915&quot; data-start=&quot;891&quot;&gt;
			&lt;li data-end=&quot;915&quot; data-start=&quot;891&quot;&gt;
			&lt;p data-end=&quot;915&quot; data-start=&quot;893&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-end=&quot;915&quot; data-start=&quot;893&quot;&gt;Bangladesh (130th)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
			&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;/ul&gt;
		&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li data-end=&quot;1026&quot; data-start=&quot;918&quot;&gt;
		&lt;p data-end=&quot;945&quot; data-start=&quot;920&quot;&gt;Ranked &lt;strong data-end=&quot;942&quot; data-start=&quot;927&quot;&gt;below India&lt;/strong&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;

		&lt;ul data-end=&quot;1026&quot; data-start=&quot;950&quot;&gt;
			&lt;li data-end=&quot;971&quot; data-start=&quot;950&quot;&gt;
			&lt;p data-end=&quot;971&quot; data-start=&quot;952&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-end=&quot;969&quot; data-start=&quot;952&quot;&gt;Nepal (145th)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
			&lt;/li&gt;
			&lt;li data-end=&quot;999&quot; data-start=&quot;976&quot;&gt;
			&lt;p data-end=&quot;999&quot; data-start=&quot;978&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-end=&quot;997&quot; data-start=&quot;978&quot;&gt;Myanmar (149th)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
			&lt;/li&gt;
			&lt;li data-end=&quot;1026&quot; data-start=&quot;1004&quot;&gt;
			&lt;p data-end=&quot;1026&quot; data-start=&quot;1006&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-end=&quot;1026&quot; data-start=&quot;1006&quot;&gt;Pakistan (168th)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
			&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;/ul&gt;
		&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li data-end=&quot;1287&quot; data-start=&quot;1027&quot;&gt;
	&lt;p data-end=&quot;1063&quot; data-start=&quot;1029&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-end=&quot;1062&quot; data-start=&quot;1029&quot;&gt;Human Development Index (HDI)&lt;/strong&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;

	&lt;ul data-end=&quot;1287&quot; data-start=&quot;1066&quot;&gt;
		&lt;li data-end=&quot;1287&quot; data-start=&quot;1066&quot;&gt;
		&lt;p data-end=&quot;1117&quot; data-start=&quot;1068&quot;&gt;Measures &lt;strong data-end=&quot;1116&quot; data-start=&quot;1077&quot;&gt;achievement in three key dimensions&lt;/strong&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;

		&lt;ol data-end=&quot;1287&quot; data-start=&quot;1122&quot;&gt;
			&lt;li data-end=&quot;1164&quot; data-start=&quot;1122&quot;&gt;
			&lt;p data-end=&quot;1164&quot; data-start=&quot;1125&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-end=&quot;1135&quot; data-start=&quot;1125&quot;&gt;Health&lt;/strong&gt; &amp;ndash; Life expectancy at birth&lt;/p&gt;
			&lt;/li&gt;
			&lt;li data-end=&quot;1232&quot; data-start=&quot;1169&quot;&gt;
			&lt;p data-end=&quot;1232&quot; data-start=&quot;1172&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-end=&quot;1185&quot; data-start=&quot;1172&quot;&gt;Education&lt;/strong&gt; &amp;ndash; Expected years and mean years of schooling&lt;/p&gt;
			&lt;/li&gt;
			&lt;li data-end=&quot;1287&quot; data-start=&quot;1237&quot;&gt;
			&lt;p data-end=&quot;1287&quot; data-start=&quot;1240&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-end=&quot;1262&quot; data-start=&quot;1240&quot;&gt;Standard of living&lt;/strong&gt; &amp;ndash; GNI per capita (PPP $)&lt;/p&gt;
			&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;/ol&gt;
		&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li data-end=&quot;1374&quot; data-start=&quot;1288&quot;&gt;
	&lt;p data-end=&quot;1374&quot; data-start=&quot;1290&quot;&gt;Developed by &lt;strong data-end=&quot;1320&quot; data-start=&quot;1303&quot;&gt;Mahbub ul Haq&lt;/strong&gt;, based on the &lt;strong data-end=&quot;1373&quot; data-start=&quot;1335&quot;&gt;capability approach of Amartya Sen&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;सही उत्तर &lt;u&gt;&lt;strong&gt;130वाँ&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/u&gt; है।&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/in_news.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;In News&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;संयुक्त राष्ट्र विकास कार्यक्रम (UNDP) की 2025 की रिपोर्ट के अनुसार, भारत मानव विकास सूचकांक में 130वें स्थान पर है।&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/key-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li data-end=&quot;311&quot; data-start=&quot;245&quot;&gt;
	&lt;p data-end=&quot;311&quot; data-start=&quot;247&quot;&gt;2025 HDR में भारत 193 देशों में से &lt;strong data-end=&quot;290&quot; data-start=&quot;260&quot;&gt;130वें स्थान&lt;/strong&gt; पर रहा।&lt;/p&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li data-end=&quot;396&quot; data-start=&quot;312&quot;&gt;
	&lt;p data-end=&quot;396&quot; data-start=&quot;314&quot;&gt;रिपोर्ट का शीर्षक: &lt;strong data-end=&quot;395&quot; data-start=&quot;328&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;एक चुनाव का मामला: AI के युग में लोग और संभावनाएँ&amp;quot;&lt;/strong&gt;।&lt;/p&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li data-end=&quot;464&quot; data-start=&quot;397&quot;&gt;
	&lt;p data-end=&quot;464&quot; data-start=&quot;399&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-end=&quot;463&quot; data-start=&quot;416&quot;&gt;संयुक्त राष्ट्र विकास कार्यक्रम (UNDP)&lt;/strong&gt; द्वारा प्रकाशित।&lt;/p&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li data-end=&quot;534&quot; data-start=&quot;465&quot;&gt;
	&lt;p data-end=&quot;534&quot; data-start=&quot;467&quot;&gt;भारत का &lt;strong data-end=&quot;491&quot; data-start=&quot;475&quot;&gt;HDI में सुधार&lt;/strong&gt; हुआ है &lt;strong data-end=&quot;513&quot; data-start=&quot;497&quot;&gt;0.676 (2022)&lt;/strong&gt; से &lt;strong data-end=&quot;533&quot; data-start=&quot;517&quot;&gt;0.685 (2023)&lt;/strong&gt; तक।&lt;/p&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li data-end=&quot;645&quot; data-start=&quot;535&quot;&gt;
	&lt;p data-end=&quot;562&quot; data-start=&quot;537&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-end=&quot;561&quot; data-start=&quot;537&quot;&gt;शीर्ष रैंक वाले देश&lt;/strong&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;

	&lt;ul data-end=&quot;645&quot; data-start=&quot;565&quot;&gt;
		&lt;li data-end=&quot;600&quot; data-start=&quot;565&quot;&gt;
		&lt;p data-end=&quot;600&quot; data-start=&quot;567&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-end=&quot;574&quot; data-start=&quot;567&quot;&gt;प्रथम&lt;/strong&gt;: आइसलैंड (HDI: &lt;strong data-end=&quot;599&quot; data-start=&quot;590&quot;&gt;0.972&lt;/strong&gt;)&lt;/p&gt;
		&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li data-end=&quot;620&quot; data-start=&quot;603&quot;&gt;
		&lt;p data-end=&quot;620&quot; data-start=&quot;605&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-end=&quot;612&quot; data-start=&quot;605&quot;&gt;द्वितीय&lt;/strong&gt;: नॉर्वे&lt;/p&gt;
		&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li data-end=&quot;645&quot; data-start=&quot;623&quot;&gt;
		&lt;p data-end=&quot;645&quot; data-start=&quot;625&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-end=&quot;632&quot; data-start=&quot;625&quot;&gt;तृतीय&lt;/strong&gt;: स्विट्ज़रलैंड&lt;/p&gt;
		&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li data-end=&quot;706&quot; data-start=&quot;646&quot;&gt;
	&lt;p data-end=&quot;706&quot; data-start=&quot;648&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-end=&quot;665&quot; data-start=&quot;648&quot;&gt;सबसे कम रैंक वाला&lt;/strong&gt;: &lt;strong data-end=&quot;682&quot; data-start=&quot;667&quot;&gt;दक्षिण सूडान&lt;/strong&gt; (193वाँ, HDI: &lt;strong data-end=&quot;705&quot; data-start=&quot;696&quot;&gt;0.388&lt;/strong&gt;)&lt;/p&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li data-end=&quot;1026&quot; data-start=&quot;707&quot;&gt;
	&lt;p data-end=&quot;744&quot; data-start=&quot;709&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-end=&quot;743&quot; data-start=&quot;709&quot;&gt;भारत के पड़ोसी देश&lt;/strong&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;

	&lt;ul data-end=&quot;1026&quot; data-start=&quot;747&quot;&gt;
		&lt;li data-end=&quot;853&quot; data-start=&quot;747&quot;&gt;
		&lt;p data-end=&quot;774&quot; data-start=&quot;749&quot;&gt;भारत से &lt;strong data-end=&quot;771&quot; data-start=&quot;756&quot;&gt;ऊपर रैंक वाले&lt;/strong&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;

		&lt;ul data-end=&quot;853&quot; data-start=&quot;779&quot;&gt;
			&lt;li data-end=&quot;799&quot; data-start=&quot;779&quot;&gt;
			&lt;p data-end=&quot;799&quot; data-start=&quot;781&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-end=&quot;797&quot; data-start=&quot;781&quot;&gt;चीन (75वाँ)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
